import React from 'react'
import { Navbar, Nav } from 'react-bootstrap'

const SideMenu = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Navbar collapseOnSelect expand="lg" defaultActiveKey="/home" className="flex-column" id="side-menu">
                <Nav.Link href="/home">Dashboard</Nav.Link>
                <Nav.Link eventKey="">Expenses Filed</Nav.Link>
                <Nav.Link eventKey="">Analytics</Nav.Link>
            </Navbar>
      
        </>
    )
}

export default SideMenu
